dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Henry Ross. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Virginia. Could you provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six two three four and my date of birth is August thirtieth, nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you, Virginia. One more piece of information needed - could you confirm the make and model of your car as listed on your policy?
Of course, my car is a two zero one eight Toyota Camry.
Great, thank you for providing that information, Virginia. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Virginia. Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day.
